MTN/VDF fiber interconnection at Kintampo

2.	MTN Fibre Assets (Kumasi – Tamale)


2.1	MTN will build an underground ducted fibre route between Kumasi (lat 06°40'26.11"N,
 long 001°37'8.97"W) and Tamale (lat 09°25'4.80"N, long 000°51'36.05"W) together with seven (7) access points located as listed in  Appendix (C). The approximate length of this route is 481km.
